  "name": "Account Settings – Overview",
  "body": "<p><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"341\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountDetails.05T5g00000IASudEAH.png\" width=\"693\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 341px; width: 693px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountDetails.05T5g00000IASudEAH.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountDetails.05T5g00000IASudEAH.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountDetails.05T5g00000IASudEAH.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountDetails.05T5g00000IASudEAH.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountDetails.05T5g00000IASudEAH.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountDetails.05T5g00000IASudEAH.png 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/AccountDetails.05T5g00000IASudEAH.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/> </p>\n<p>Click your username on the top-right corner of the application and then select Account Settings. The Account Settings page has the following tabs - each covering specific areas of account management:</p>\n<ul><li><b>ACCOUNT(S)</b>: View and update your company information. Add and manage multiple accounts. See <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Manage-Your-JetSend-Accounts\">Manage Your JetSend Accounts</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Multi-Account-Management\">Multi-Account Management</a>.</li><li><strong>PROFILE</strong>: Manage your personal and login information. See <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Manage-Your-JetSend-Profile\">Manage Your JetSend Profile</a>.</li><li><strong>USERS:</strong> Add new users and manage existing users in your account. See <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Add-and-Manage-Users-in-JetSend\">Add and Manage Users in JetSend</a>.</li><li><strong>PLAN:</strong> View details of your existing plan and usage information. Manage your subscription plan and add-ons such as dedicated IP. See <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/JetSend-Subscription-Plan\">JetSend Subscription Plan</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/JetSend-billing-details\">JetSend Billing Details</a>.</li><li><strong>API KEYS:</strong> Create and manage API Keys and Master API Key. See <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Create-and-Manage-API-Keys-in-JetSend\">Create and Manage API Keys in JetSend</a>.</li></ul>",
